RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT dd.contract_ref_no CONTRACT_REF_NO,dd.Counterparty COUNTERPARTY,dd.contract_ccy CCY,(SELECT Principal_Outstanding_Bal FROM Oltbs_Contract_Balance WHERE Contract_Ref_No = dd.contract_ref_no) PRINCIPALOUTSTANDINGBAL,dd.Book_date VALUEDATE, aa.maturity_date MATURITYDATE,dd.branch BRANCH, (SELECT CUSTOMER_NAME1 FROM oltms_customer WHERE CUSTOMER_NO = dd.Counterparty) CUSTNAME,aa.amount_financed AMOUNT,aa.facility_name FACILITYNAME, (SELECT ADDL_TEXT FROM OLTBS_ADDL_TEXT D WHERE D.REFERENCE_NO = bb.contract_ref_no AND D.EVNT_SEQ_NO = bb.event_seq_no) ADDLTEXT FROM OLtbs_contract dd, Oltbs_contract_event_log bb,(select x.contract_ref_no,x.amount_financed, x.facility_name, x.maturity_date From oltbs_contract_master x where x.version_no = (select max(om.version_no) from Oltbs_contract_master om WHERE om.contract_ref_no = x.contract_ref_no) UNION select y.contract_ref_no,y.amount,y.facility_name,y.facility_end_date From Lbtbs_syndication_master y where y.version_no = (select max(lsm.version_no) from Lbtbs_syndication_master lsm WHERE lsm.contract_ref_no = y.contract_ref_no)) aa WHERE dd.contract_ref_no = bb.contract_ref_no AND bb.event_seq_no = dd.latest_event_seq_no AND dd.contract_ref_no = aa.contract_ref_no(+) AND dd.contract_ref_no IN (SELECT DISTINCT cc.contract_ref_no FROM OLtbs_contract cc WHERE cc.module_code IN ('FC', 'LB') AND cc.contract_status = 'L' AND /*cc.auth_status = 'A'*/ (cc.auth_status = 'A' or (cc.auth_status = 'U' AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM oltb_contract_event_log ae WHERE ae.contract_ref_no = cc.contract_ref_no AND ae.event_code = 'MRKA' AND ae.auth_status = 'U' ORDER BY EVENT_SEQ_NO DESC FETCH FIRST 1 Rows ONLY))) AND cc.contract_ref_no NOT IN (SELECT a.contract_ref_no contract_ref_no FROM OLtbs_contract_split_rollover a WHERE a.contract_ref_no = cc.contract_ref_no AND a.version_no = (SELECT MAX(version_no) FROM OLtbs_contract_split_rollover WHERE contract_ref_no = a.contract_ref_no) AND a.rollover_contract_ref_no IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT b.child_ref_no contract_ref_no FROM lBtb_contract_consol_master a, lBtb_contract_consol_detail b WHERE a.contract_ref_no = b.contract_ref_no AND b.child_ref_no = cc.contract_ref_no AND a.rollover_contract_ref_no IS NOT NULL AND /*a.auth_stat = 'A'*/ (a.auth_stat = 'A' or (a.auth_stat = 'U' AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM oltb_contract_event_log ae WHERE ae.contract_ref_no = cc.contract_ref_no AND ae.event_code = 'MRKA' AND ae.auth_status = 'U' ORDER BY EVENT_SEQ_NO DESC FETCH FIRST 1 Rows ONLY))) AND a.record_stat = 'O' UNION SELECT a.contract_ref_no contract_ref_no FROM lBtb_contract_split_detail a WHERE a.contract_ref_no = cc.contract_ref_no AND a.split_ref_no IS NOT NULL UNION SELECT b.child_ref_no contract_ref_no FROM lBtbs_contract_merge_master a, lBtbs_contract_merge_detail b WHERE a.contract_ref_no = b.contract_ref_no AND b.child_ref_no = cc.contract_ref_no AND a.merge_status = 'P' AND /*a.auth_stat = 'A'*/ (a.auth_stat = 'A' or (a.auth_stat = 'U' AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM oltb_contract_event_log ae WHERE ae.contract_ref_no = cc.contract_ref_no AND ae.event_code = 'MRKA' AND ae.auth_status = 'U' ORDER BY EVENT_SEQ_NO DESC FETCH FIRST 1 Rows ONLY))) AND a.record_stat = 'O'))
